title: Environmental Operations (Military Tactics)
description:
This is an assortment of army manuals and literature, teaching how to fight effectively in various conditions:
-Cold Weather
-Desert
-Marine
-Mountains
-Urban
-Woodland

There is also literature on the subject in general, and a folder on navigation and topography.  This is certainly one of those torrents worth keeping, burning to a disc, and stashing away.
